{"tid":2517310,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"內地婚姻家庭案件判決(相互承認及強制執行)條例，立法會正式三讀通過","createTime":"2021-05-05T08:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T09:12:30.000Z","uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"13d697d17a6cdb24044299eccafec44251592112","tid":2517310,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:50:02.000Z","msg":"無人關注及討論？"},{"pid":"3c9a8d77eaeaba58d194e2644b9cef3b02dbccd3","tid":2517310,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:53:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr20-21/chinese/bc/bc101/general/bc101.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr20-21%2Fchinese%2Fbc%2Fbc101%2Fgeneral%2Fbc101.htm&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=72cfed06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr20-21/chinese/bc/bc101/general/bc101.htm</a>"},{"pid":"42b9b60c4cf557fdf82a8a3ad176e83152af2fe4","tid":2517310,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:59:55.000Z","msg":"《條例草案》將會適用於條例生效日期當日或之後，由內地法院或香港法院在婚姻或家庭案件中作出的判決，以及於生效日期當日或之後發出的內地離婚證。《條例草案》主要訂立登記機制，供一方當事人在<strong><span class=\"red\">香港法院申請承認和強制執行內地婚姻或家庭案件判決中的指明命令</span></strong>，或申請<strong><span class=\"red\">承認內地民政部門發出的離婚證。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n　　至於<strong><span class=\"red\">內地法院承認或強制執行香港的婚姻或家庭案件判決方面</span></strong>，<strong><span class=\"red\">將由最高人民法院發布司法解釋實施《安排》</span></strong>。為了便利香港婚姻或家庭案件判決的當事人，向內地法院申請承認和強制執行香港判決，《條例草案》亦訂立機制，讓香港判決的一方，可向香港法院申請香港判決的經核證文本及證明書。<br />\n<br />\n正如在動議二讀發言時已提及，其中對當事人十分重要的包括在新機制下，一旦有香港兒童被一方父母不當地遷移到或扣留在內地的情況，另一方可以根據香港法院作出的相關命令，尋求內地法院協助交還或交付。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202105/05/P2021050500510.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202105%2F05%2FP2021050500510.htm&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=ac4fac6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202105/05/P2021050500510.htm</a>"},{"pid":"311c058e3248f518878977145e330e04bed45adc","tid":2517310,"uid":11663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:09:13.000Z","msg":"係咪即係可以被離婚被分身家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2753129c1b680d40060d379d8b25e42e636e6207","tid":2517310,"uid":158633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:10:43.000Z","msg":"重婚罪假結婚果啲拉唔拉先"},{"pid":"8e6c17d6269b2ac99193a9fe64c0eb61e788864d","tid":2517310,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"311c058e3248f518878977145e330e04bed45adc","tid":2517310,"uid":11663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:09:13.000Z","msg":"係咪即係可以被離婚被分身家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:11:11.000Z","msg":"正確應該係類似逃犯條例修訂的（家事及婚姻）版本"},{"pid":"ef1395f3e55bad5b822b972f53281306516ead0d","tid":2517310,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2753129c1b680d40060d379d8b25e42e636e6207","tid":2517310,"uid":158633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:10:43.000Z","msg":"重婚罪假結婚果啲拉唔拉先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:12:30.000Z","msg":"互相承認及強制執行喎"}]}